cdata.name: Brazio
cdata.desc: Brazio is a decentralised financial ecosystem that seeks to increase the number of people with access to a secure, decentralised bank account through the development of a cryptocurrency which removes entities like banks and supports rapid transactions with low fees. The Brazio coin is a fork of the Bitcoin source code on March 2018, inherited all the features of bitcoin's blockchain and due to the PoW system enables the network participants to mine the digital currency BRAZ.
